            {
               "text": "<p><hr /></p><p>Teaching goes beyond simply presenting information for memorization, as shown by a survey with teachers and students that validates the need for homework as a way to reinforce knowledge (<htcite0>).</p><p>In order to assist in this mission, this page offers free educational games and applications.</p><p><b>The games can be updated at any time. <span id=\"family_common_sn\"></span></b></p>",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "0e18261e-e542-4bd1-a074-a42b9c0eb25d",
